    "Details": "A very mobile design thanks to its 250-Rated extra-light fusion engine and the use of a TSM in its construction. A number of weapons are mounted in its turret, including a heavy PPC, light PPC, and one of the 'Mech's two ER medium lasers. Its other ER medium laser is installed in the 'Mech's center torso, with the Beagle Active Probe, and a ER small laser is mounted in its head. To take advantage of the 'Mech's TSM, each leg actuator is fitted with spikes\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Quad Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.99</color></b>",
